# Booking notifications ---------------------------------------------------
# The booking system emails the studio whenever a passport/visa slot is booked.
# With NO key set (default), it logs to the console and data/notifications.log
# so the demo runs with zero secrets. To send real email, set a Resend key:
#
#   RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
#
# Where alerts go (defaults shown):
#   NOTIFY_TO=takphoto.inc@gmail.com
#   NOTIFY_FROM=Photo Tak Bookings <bookings@takphoto.ca>
#
# NOTE: Resend (or any provider) requires a verified sending domain for the
# NOTIFY_FROM address. Until takphoto.ca is verified, keep NOTIFY_FROM on a
# resend.dev test sender.
